{"snp3.9:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 3.9 ","snp3.9:0.2":"Vasetthasutta ","snp3.9:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp3.9:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava icchanangale viharati icchanangalavanasande. ","snp3.9:1.3":"Tena kho pana samayena sambahula abhinnata abhinnata brahmanamahasala icchanangale pativasanti, seyyathidam—","snp3.9:1.4":"canki brahmano, tarukkho brahmano, pokkharasati brahmano, janussoni brahmano, todeyyo brahmano, anne ca abhinnata abhinnata brahmanamahasala. ","snp3.9:1.5":"Atha kho vasetthabharadvajanam manavanam janghaviharam anucankamantanam anuvicarantanam ayamantarakatha udapadi: ","snp3.9:1.6":"“katham, bho, brahmano hoti”ti? ","snp3.9:2.1":"Bharadvajo manavo evamaha: ","snp3.9:2.2":"“yato kho, bho, ubhato sujato hoti matito ca pitito ca samsuddhagahaniko yava sattama pitamahayuga akkhitto anupakkuttho jativadena, ","snp3.9:2.3":"ettavata kho bho brahmano hoti”ti. ","snp3.9:3.1":"Vasettho manavo evamaha: ","snp3.9:3.2":"“yato kho, bho, silava ca hoti vatasampanno ca, ","snp3.9:3.3":"ettavata kho, bho, brahmano hoti”ti. ","snp3.9:3.4":"Neva kho asakkhi bharadvajo manavo vasettham manavam sannapetum, na pana asakkhi vasettho manavo bharadvajam manavam sannapetum. ","snp3.9:4.1":"Atha kho vasettho manavo bharadvajam manavam amantesi: ","snp3.9:4.2":"“ayam kho, bho bharadvaja, samano gotamo sakyaputto sakyakula pabbajito icchanangale viharati icchanangalavanasande; ","snp3.9:4.3":"tam kho pana bhavantam gotamam evam kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggato: ","snp3.9:4.4":"‘itipi …pe… buddho bhagava’ti. ","snp3.9:4.5":"Ayama, bho bharadvaja, yena samano gotamo tenupasankamissama; upasankamitva samanam gotamam etamattham pucchissama. ","snp3.9:4.6":"Yatha no samano gotamo byakarissati tatha nam dharessama”ti. ","snp3.9:4.7":"“Evam, bho”ti kho bharadvajo manavo vasetthassa manavassa paccassosi. ","snp3.9:5.1":"Atha kho vasetthabharadvaja manava yena bhagava tenupasankamimsu; upasankamitva bhagavata saddhim sammodimsu. ","snp3.9:5.2":"Sammodaniyam katham saraniyam vitisaretva ekamantam nisidimsu. ","snp3.9:5.3":"Ekamantam nisinno kho vasettho manavo bhagavantam gathahi ajjhabhasi: ","snp3.9:6.1":"“Anunnatapatinnata, ","snp3.9:6.2":"tevijja mayamasmubho; ","snp3.9:6.3":"Aham pokkharasatissa, ","snp3.9:6.4":"tarukkhassayam manavo. ","snp3.9:7.1":"Tevijjanam yadakkhatam, ","snp3.9:7.2":"Tatra kevalinosmase; ","snp3.9:7.3":"Padakasma veyyakarana, ","snp3.9:7.4":"Jappe acariyasadisa. ","snp3.9:8.1":"Tesam no jativadasmim, ","snp3.9:8.2":"vivado atthi gotama; ","snp3.9:8.3":"Jatiya brahmano hoti, ","snp3.9:8.4":"bharadvajo iti bhasati; ","snp3.9:8.5":"Ahanca kammuna brumi, ","snp3.9:8.6":"evam janahi cakkhuma. ","snp3.9:9.1":"Te na sakkoma sannapetum, ","snp3.9:9.2":"annamannam mayam ubho; ","snp3.9:9.3":"Bhavantam putthumagamha, ","snp3.9:9.4":"sambuddham iti vissutam. ","snp3.9:10.1":"Candam yatha khayatitam, ","snp3.9:10.2":"pecca panjalika jana; ","snp3.9:10.3":"Vandamana namassanti, ","snp3.9:10.4":"evam lokasmi gotamam. ","snp3.9:11.1":"Cakkhum loke samuppannam, ","snp3.9:11.2":"mayam pucchama gotamam; ","snp3.9:11.3":"Jatiya brahmano hoti, ","snp3.9:11.4":"udahu bhavati kammuna; ","snp3.9:11.5":"Ajanatam no pabruhi, ","snp3.9:11.6":"yatha janemu brahmanam”. ","snp3.9:12.1":"“Tesam vo aham byakkhissam, ","snp3.9:12.2":"(vasetthati bhagava) ","snp3.9:12.3":"Anupubbam yathatatham; ","snp3.9:12.4":"Jativibhangam pananam, ","snp3.9:12.5":"Annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:13.1":"Tinarukkhepi janatha, ","snp3.9:13.2":"na capi patijanare; ","snp3.9:13.3":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","snp3.9:13.4":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:14.1":"Tato kite patange ca, ","snp3.9:14.2":"yava kunthakipillike; ","snp3.9:14.3":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","snp3.9:14.4":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:15.1":"Catuppadepi janatha, ","snp3.9:15.2":"Khuddake ca mahallake; ","snp3.9:15.3":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","snp3.9:15.4":"Annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:16.1":"Padudarepi janatha, ","snp3.9:16.2":"Urage dighapitthike; ","snp3.9:16.3":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","snp3.9:16.4":"Annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:17.1":"Tato macchepi janatha, ","snp3.9:17.2":"Odake varigocare; ","snp3.9:17.3":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","snp3.9:17.4":"Annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:18.1":"Tato pakkhipi janatha, ","snp3.9:18.2":"Pattayane vihangame; ","snp3.9:18.3":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","snp3.9:18.4":"Annamanna hi jatiyo. ","snp3.9:19.1":"Yatha etasu jatisu, ","snp3.9:19.2":"Lingam jatimayam puthu; ","snp3.9:19.3":"Evam natthi manussesu, ","snp3.9:19.4":"Lingam jatimayam puthu. ","snp3.9:20.1":"Na kesehi na sisena, ","snp3.9:20.2":"Na kannehi na akkhibhi; ","snp3.9:20.3":"Na mukhena na nasaya, ","snp3.9:20.4":"Na otthehi bhamuhi va. ","snp3.9:21.1":"Na givaya na amsehi, ","snp3.9:21.2":"Na udarena na pitthiya; ","snp3.9:21.3":"Na soniya na urasa, ","snp3.9:21.4":"Na sambadhe na methune. ","snp3.9:22.1":"Na hatthehi na padehi, ","snp3.9:22.2":"Nangulihi nakhehi va; ","snp3.9:22.3":"Na janghahi na uruhi, ","snp3.9:22.4":"Na vannena sarena va; ","snp3.9:22.5":"Lingam jatimayam neva, ","snp3.9:22.6":"Yatha annasu jatisu. ","snp3.9:23.1":"Paccattanca sariresu, ","snp3.9:23.2":"Manussesvetam na vijjati; ","snp3.9:23.3":"Vokaranca manussesu, ","snp3.9:23.4":"Samannaya pavuccati. ","snp3.9:24.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:24.2":"Gorakkham upajivati; ","snp3.9:24.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:24.4":"Kassako so na brahmano. ","snp3.9:25.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:25.2":"Puthusippena jivati; ","snp3.9:25.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:25.4":"Sippiko so na brahmano. ","snp3.9:26.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:26.2":"Voharam upajivati; ","snp3.9:26.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:26.4":"Vanijo so na brahmano. ","snp3.9:27.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:27.2":"Parapessena jivati; ","snp3.9:27.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:27.4":"Pessiko so na brahmano. ","snp3.9:28.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:28.2":"Adinnam upajivati; ","snp3.9:28.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:28.4":"Coro eso na brahmano. ","snp3.9:29.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:29.2":"Issattham upajivati; ","snp3.9:29.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:29.4":"Yodhajivo na brahmano. ","snp3.9:30.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:30.2":"Porohiccena jivati; ","snp3.9:30.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:30.4":"Yajako eso na brahmano. ","snp3.9:31.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","snp3.9:31.2":"Gamam ratthanca bhunjati; ","snp3.9:31.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:31.4":"Raja eso na brahmano. ","snp3.9:32.1":"Na caham brahmanam brumi, ","snp3.9:32.2":"Yonijam mattisambhavam; ","snp3.9:32.3":"Bhovadi nama so hoti, ","snp3.9:32.4":"Sace hoti sakincano; ","snp3.9:32.5":"Akincanam anadanam, ","snp3.9:32.6":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:33.1":"Sabbasamyojanam chetva, ","snp3.9:33.2":"Yo ve na paritassati; ","snp3.9:33.3":"Sangatigam visamyuttam, ","snp3.9:33.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:34.1":"Chetva naddhim varattanca, ","snp3.9:34.2":"Sandanam sahanukkamam; ","snp3.9:34.3":"Ukkhittapaligham buddham, ","snp3.9:34.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:35.1":"Akkosam vadhabandhanca, ","snp3.9:35.2":"Aduttho yo titikkhati; ","snp3.9:35.3":"Khantibalam balanikam, ","snp3.9:35.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:36.1":"Akkodhanam vatavantam, ","snp3.9:36.2":"Silavantam anussadam; ","snp3.9:36.3":"Dantam antimasariram, ","snp3.9:36.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:37.1":"Vari pokkharapatteva, ","snp3.9:37.2":"Araggeriva sasapo; ","snp3.9:37.3":"Yo na limpati kamesu, ","snp3.9:37.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:38.1":"Yo dukkhassa pajanati, ","snp3.9:38.2":"Idheva khayamattano; ","snp3.9:38.3":"Pannabharam visamyuttam, ","snp3.9:38.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:39.1":"Gambhirapannam medhavim, ","snp3.9:39.2":"Maggamaggassa kovidam; ","snp3.9:39.3":"Uttamatthamanuppattam, ","snp3.9:39.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:40.1":"Asamsattham gahatthehi, ","snp3.9:40.2":"Anagarehi cubhayam; ","snp3.9:40.3":"Anokasarimappiccham, ","snp3.9:40.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:41.1":"Nidhaya dandam bhutesu, ","snp3.9:41.2":"Tasesu thavaresu ca; ","snp3.9:41.3":"Yo na hanti na ghateti, ","snp3.9:41.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:42.1":"Aviruddham viruddhesu, ","snp3.9:42.2":"Attadandesu nibbutam; ","snp3.9:42.3":"Sadanesu anadanam, ","snp3.9:42.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:43.1":"Yassa rago ca doso ca, ","snp3.9:43.2":"Mano makkho ca patito; ","snp3.9:43.3":"Sasaporiva aragga, ","snp3.9:43.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:44.1":"Akakkasam vinnapanim, ","snp3.9:44.2":"Giram saccamudiraye; ","snp3.9:44.3":"Yaya nabhisaje kanci, ","snp3.9:44.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:45.1":"Yodha digham va rassam va, ","snp3.9:45.2":"Anum thulam subhasubham; ","snp3.9:45.3":"Loke adinnam nadiyati, ","snp3.9:45.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:46.1":"Asa yassa na vijjanti, ","snp3.9:46.2":"Asmim loke paramhi ca; ","snp3.9:46.3":"Nirasasam visamyuttam, ","snp3.9:46.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:47.1":"Yassalaya na vijjanti, ","snp3.9:47.2":"Annaya akathankathi; ","snp3.9:47.3":"Amatogadhamanuppattam, ","snp3.9:47.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:48.1":"Yodha punnanca papanca, ","snp3.9:48.2":"Ubho sangamupaccaga; ","snp3.9:48.3":"Asokam virajam suddham, ","snp3.9:48.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:49.1":"Candamva vimalam suddham, ","snp3.9:49.2":"Vippasannamanavilam; ","snp3.9:49.3":"Nandibhavaparikkhinam, ","snp3.9:49.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:50.1":"Yomam palipatham duggam, ","snp3.9:50.2":"Samsaram mohamaccaga; ","snp3.9:50.3":"Tinno parangato jhayi, ","snp3.9:50.4":"Anejo akathankathi; ","snp3.9:50.5":"Anupadaya nibbuto, ","snp3.9:50.6":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:51.1":"Yodha kame pahantvana, ","snp3.9:51.2":"Anagaro paribbaje; ","snp3.9:51.3":"Kamabhavaparikkhinam, ","snp3.9:51.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:52.1":"Yodha tanham pahantvana, ","snp3.9:52.2":"Anagaro paribbaje; ","snp3.9:52.3":"Tanhabhavaparikkhinam, ","snp3.9:52.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:53.1":"Hitva manusakam yogam, ","snp3.9:53.2":"Dibbam yogam upaccaga; ","snp3.9:53.3":"Sabbayogavisamyuttam, ","snp3.9:53.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:54.1":"Hitva ratinca aratim, ","snp3.9:54.2":"Sitibhutam nirupadhim; ","snp3.9:54.3":"Sabbalokabhibhum viram, ","snp3.9:54.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:55.1":"Cutim yo vedi sattanam, ","snp3.9:55.2":"Upapattinca sabbaso; ","snp3.9:55.3":"Asattam sugatam buddham, ","snp3.9:55.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:56.1":"Yassa gatim na jananti, ","snp3.9:56.2":"Deva gandhabbamanusa; ","snp3.9:56.3":"Khinasavam arahantam, ","snp3.9:56.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:57.1":"Yassa pure ca paccha ca, ","snp3.9:57.2":"Majjhe ca natthi kincanam; ","snp3.9:57.3":"Akincanam anadanam, ","snp3.9:57.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:58.1":"Usabham pavaram viram, ","snp3.9:58.2":"Mahesim vijitavinam; ","snp3.9:58.3":"Anejam nhatakam buddham, ","snp3.9:58.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:59.1":"Pubbenivasam yo vedi, ","snp3.9:59.2":"Saggapayanca passati; ","snp3.9:59.3":"Atho jatikkhayam patto, ","snp3.9:59.4":"Tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","snp3.9:60.1":"Samanna hesa lokasmim, ","snp3.9:60.2":"Namagottam pakappitam; ","snp3.9:60.3":"Sammucca samudagatam, ","snp3.9:60.4":"Tattha tattha pakappitam. ","snp3.9:61.1":"Digharattamanusayitam, ","snp3.9:61.2":"Ditthigatamajanatam; ","snp3.9:61.3":"Ajananta no pabruvanti, ","snp3.9:61.4":"Jatiya hoti brahmano. ","snp3.9:62.1":"Na jacca brahmano hoti, ","snp3.9:62.2":"Na jacca hoti abrahmano; ","snp3.9:62.3":"Kammuna brahmano hoti, ","snp3.9:62.4":"Kammuna hoti abrahmano. ","snp3.9:63.1":"Kassako kammuna hoti, ","snp3.9:63.2":"Sippiko hoti kammuna; ","snp3.9:63.3":"Vanijo kammuna hoti, ","snp3.9:63.4":"Pessiko hoti kammuna. ","snp3.9:64.1":"Coropi kammuna hoti, ","snp3.9:64.2":"Yodhajivopi kammuna; ","snp3.9:64.3":"Yajako kammuna hoti, ","snp3.9:64.4":"Rajapi hoti kammuna. ","snp3.9:65.1":"Evametam yathabhutam, ","snp3.9:65.2":"Kammam passanti pandita; ","snp3.9:65.3":"Paticcasamuppadadassa, ","snp3.9:65.4":"Kammavipakakovida. ","snp3.9:66.1":"Kammuna vattati loko, ","snp3.9:66.2":"Kammuna vattati paja; ","snp3.9:66.3":"Kammanibandhana satta, ","snp3.9:66.4":"Rathassaniva yayato. ","snp3.9:67.1":"Tapena brahmacariyena, ","snp3.9:67.2":"Samyamena damena ca; ","snp3.9:67.3":"Etena brahmano hoti, ","snp3.9:67.4":"Etam brahmanamuttamam. ","snp3.9:68.1":"Tihi vijjahi sampanno, ","snp3.9:68.2":"santo khinapunabbhavo; ","snp3.9:68.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","snp3.9:68.4":"brahma sakko vijanatan”ti. ","snp3.9:69.1":"Evam vutte, vasetthabharadvaja manava bhagavantam etadavocum: ","snp3.9:69.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama …pe… ","snp3.9:69.3":"upasake no bhavam gotamo dharetu ajjatagge panupete saranam gate”ti. ","snp3.9:69.4":"Vasetthasuttam navamam. "}